OL,6,FA man who stabbed his brother in the
OL,7,Fheart, has been found guilty of murder
OL,8,Ffollowing a 10 day trial at Lewes
OL,9,FCrown Court.
OL,11,FThe jury reached a unanimous verdict
OL,12,Fin finding 36-year-old Danny Craze,
OL,13,Ffrom West Molesey, guilty of the
OL,14,Fmurder of 26-year-old Louis Craze on
OL,15,F18 November 2023.
OL,17,FThe court heard how officers were sent
OL,18,Fto an address in Bishop Fox Way after
OL,19,Freceiving a 999 call reporting that a
OL,20,Fman had been stabbed inside a house.
