OL,6,FLouis Craze was found dead. A post-
OL,7,Fmortem determined that he had died
OL,8,Ffrom a single stab wound to the heart.
OL,10,FHis brother, Danny Craze, was arrested
OL,11,Ffor the murder of his brother that
OL,12,Fafternoon.
OL,14,FThe fatal stabbing took place
OL,15,Ffollowing a verbal altercation between
OL,16,Fthe brothers.
