OL,6,FDanny told the court that his brother
OL,7,Fwalked into the knife that he was
OL,8,Fholding to protect himself. However,
OL,9,FPolice say witness testimony, CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage and digital and forensic
OL,11,Fevidence proved that this was not the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,FPaying tribute to Louis, his family
OL,15,Fsaid, "The only word to describe how
OL,16,Fthe family is feeling is heartbroken."
